 Create a production-level SaaS web application called "GrowthForge AI"

Tagline:
"Analyze. Improve. Grow."

Mission:
Build an AI-powered business growth dashboard that helps local businesses analyze their website, discover weaknesses, compare with competitors, receive AI recommendations, and track leads.

This is NOT a simple portfolio project. Build it like a real startup product with premium UI, modern UX, scalable architecture, smooth animations, and dashboard-level interactions.

Tech stack:

Frontend:
- React
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion
- Recharts
- Axios

Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT Authentication
- Socket.io

Design Requirements:

Use a premium dark SaaS design.

Colors:

Background: #0f172a
Card: #1e293b
Accent: #6366f1
Text: white

UI Style:

- Glassmorphism
- Large rounded cards
- Soft shadows
- Animated hover effects
- Smooth page transitions
- Responsive mobile layout
- Sticky sidebar
- Dashboard feel similar to modern startup products
- Loading skeletons
- Animated progress bars
- Professional charts
- Micro interactions

